        <item>
          <title>Cubs trade for Cleveland reliever Eli Morgan; Wisdom DFA'd</title>
          <description><![CDATA[CLEVELAND, Ind. — The Cubs are trading for Cleveland relief pitcher Eli Morgan. As a result of adding Morgan to the 40-man, Patrick Wisdom was designated for assignment. Morgan, 28, had the best season of his career in 2024 with a 1.93 ERA with Cleveland in 42 innings.]]></description>
